Rating: 4
I've been using this recipe for some time now and still get raves over it. Quick, easy and delish!

Rating: 4
I have used this recipe as a base for my "three chile salsa" that I love and so does my family and friends. I add roasted anaheim peppers. I use the dried guajillo chiles and chop them up fine in a small food processor. Also, I am generous with the adobo sauce (love it). Great stuff.

