Rating: 3
This is a good, basic, non-tomato salsa that is great to flavor meat or use as a "taco sauce".

Rating: 4
I made this salsa/ pepper sauce with the pastor tacos recipe in the same issue.... the combination was delicious! Possibly better yet was the next morning when I drizzled it over top of my omelet. This is a must have for just about anything Mexican.